title: Cara Delevingne
summary: Cara Jocelyn Delevingne (/ˈkɑːrə ˌdɛləˈviːn/ KAH-rə DEL-ə-VEEN; born 12 August 1992) is an English model, actress, and singer.[5] She signed with Storm Management after leaving school in 2009.[6] Delevingne won Model of the Year at the British Fashion Awards in 2012 and 2014.[7]
